{"type": "article", "id": 12805, "title": "微型烤箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-30T07:50:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000205jevZzkDnN3RQKJH7.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tKristian Tapaninaho 推出了一款微型烤箱，可以在两分钟内完成一个 Pizza 的烧烤，而且 Pizza 会带有柴烧的味道。设计师表示其设计初衷在于希望烤箱的 Pizza 也能够带有木头烧烤的香味，烤箱使用丝网不锈钢，可以 100％ 燃烧木屑，加速烧烤过程。除了烤 Pizza，这款烤箱也可以用于其他食物的烧烤。目前产品售价 299 美元，这是<a href=\"http://uuni.net/products/uuni-2\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140518Mx8uOye27a0g9BAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140518Q4ejBRciMFztH5gK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405195LRtAw6CXSOh8lgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140519SNH6LJ8gzUYRXtC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405207A9NHI4VGfUh3EzK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405204b5eR6Vp9f1DXJCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}